    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>You may either convert the stream to <code>IntStream</code>:</p>\n\n<pre><code>OptionalInt max = list.stream().mapToInt(Integer::intValue).max();\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Or specify the natural order comparator:</p>\n\n<pre><code>Optional&lt;Integer&gt; max = list.stream().max(Comparator.naturalOrder());\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Or use reduce operation:</p>\n\n<pre><code>Optional&lt;Integer&gt; max = list.stream().reduce(Integer::max);\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Or use collector:</p>\n\n<pre><code>Optional&lt;Integer&gt; max = list.stream().collect(Collectors.maxBy(Comparator.naturalOrder()));\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Or use IntSummaryStatistics:</p>\n\n<pre><code>int max = list.stream().collect(Collectors.summarizingInt(Integer::intValue)).getMax();\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
