    "body" : "<p>I think another easy way is</p>\n<pre><code>IntSummaryStatistics statistics = List.of(1, 2, 3).stream()\n             .mapToInt(Integer::intValue)\n             .summaryStatistics();\nint max = statistics.getMax();\n\n \n</code></pre>\n<p>With this you can also <code>getMin()</code> amd other stuff like mean. A SummaryStatistics Object can be created from other Streams by supplying appropriate parameters.</p>\n"
